      534.39,
      494.5,
      548.85
    ],
    "text": "46 of 2011 were operational and enforceable on the date material to this matter?",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua",
      "BookAntiqua-Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      578.79,
      526.15,
      593.25
    ],
    "text": "2. Albeit brief, the facts applicable to understand the need for adjudication of this",
    "fonts": [
      "ArialMT",
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      601.23,
      224.69,
      615.69
    ],
    "text": "matter are as follows:",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua",
      "BookAntiqua-Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      144.02,
      623.55,
      526.29,
      638.01
    ],
    "text": "The Appellant\u2019s late husband \u2013 A.L. Kaldeen (who had passed away in",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      144.02,
      645.99,
      526.42,
      660.45
    ],
    "text": "2010), had been the owner of a paddy land known as Ambagasdoowa.",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua",
      "BookAntiqua-Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      144.02,
      668.34,
      526.12,
      682.8
    ],
    "text": "During the lifetime of the Appellant\u2019s late husband, this land had been",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      144.02,
      690.66,
      526.31,
      705.12
    ],
    "text": "cultivated by the Respondent\u2019s late father M.L.M. Karunaratne in his",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      144.02,
      713.1,
      526.33,
      727.56
    ],
    "text": "capacity as the tenant cultivator of Ambagasdoowa. Following her",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua",
      "BookAntiqua-Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      144.02,
      735.42,
      526.25,
      749.88
    ],
    "text": "husband\u2019s demise in 2010, the Appellant succeeded as the landlord of",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      144.02,
      757.86,
      526.14,
      772.32
    ],
    "text": "the paddy field. Karunaratne continued to cultivate the land under the",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      77.78,
      806.95,
      519.69,
      815.95
    ],
    "text": "SC APPEAL 133/2024 - RAIHAN UMMA VS. VINEETHA CHANDRANI \u2013 JUDGMENT 3",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      9.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      144.02,
      50.0,
      526.35,
      64.46
    ],
    "text": "Appellant. Karunaratne passed away on 13th March 2011. For a period",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      144.02,
      72.32,
      526.2,
      86.78
    ],
    "text": "of approximately 9 years preceding the death of Karunaratne, he had",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      144.02,
      94.66,
      526.28,
      109.12
    ],
    "text": "been suffering from a terminal illness, and therefore, the Respondent",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      144.02,
      117.1,
      526.4,
      131.56
    ],
    "text": "had been cultivating the land as the de-facto tenant cultivator. Following",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua",
      "BookAntiqua-Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      144.02,
      139.42,
      526.29,
      153.88
    ],
    "text": "Karunaratne\u2019s passing away, the Respondent attempted to continue",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      144.02,
      161.86,
      526.36,
      176.32
    ],
    "text": "cultivation of Ambagasdoowa on the premise that she had succeeded to",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua",
      "BookAntiqua-Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      144.02,
      184.18,
      526.4,
      198.64
    ],
    "text": "the entitlement of her father to function as the tenant cultivator. The",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      144.02,
      206.5,
      526.4,
      220.96
    ],
    "text": "Appellant resisted that move and ousted the Respondent. Thus, the",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      144.02,
      228.94,
      526.42,
      243.4
    ],
    "text": "dispute between the Appellant and the Respondent commenced. On 15th",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      144.02,
      251.26,
      526.16,
      265.72
    ],
    "text": "July 2011, the Respondent filed a complaint with the Agrarian Tribunal.",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      144.02,
      273.73,
      526.11,
      288.19
    ],
    "text": "It was while that inquiry was pending, that Act No. 46 of 2011 was",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      144.02,
      296.05,
      292.61,
      310.51
    ],
    "text": "enacted by Parliament.",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      339.85,
      176.66,
      354.11
    ],
    "text": "Legislative history",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      361.81,
      526.02,
      376.27
    ],
    "text": "3. Under and in terms of the Agrarian Services Act, No. 58 of 1979 (as amended)",
    "fonts": [
      "ArialMT",
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      384.13,
      526.38,
      398.59
    ],
    "text": "succession to tenancy of a tenant cultivator was by operation of the law. Thus,",
    "fonts": [
      "BookAntiqua"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
